parameters:
Strategist Domdora: "If I can harness the energy of this stone, my
once shattered dream will start to take on a shade of reality."
Strategist Domdora: "I see, I see! If I do this here..."

Strategist Domdora: "Just a little more, it seems I'm about to see the
whole picture."
Strategist Domdora: "What is it! You're being noisy!"

Zaider-Grunt: "My apologies. But... Po, Pony-Ceres has infiltrated
this research facility!"
Strategist Domdora: "What!? How did they find this place!?"

Zaider-Grunt: "We don't know. However, it's only a matter of time
before Pony-Ceres makes it here..."

Strategist Domdora: "Gnununun, damn Pony-Ceres! To interfere with my
research is unforgivable!"
Strategist Domdora: "Mobilize all Zaiborgs to stop them!"

Strategist Domdora: "They must not be allowed to come here at any
cost!"

Strategist Domdora: "Perhaps I should prepare for the worst-case
scenario..."
Should I open the vent and go inside?
